sent you to work for me.

591
00:26:16,350 --> 00:26:18,040
Commander Kang,

592
00:26:18,350 --> 00:26:20,190
please speak nicely of me.

593
00:26:21,110 --> 00:26:22,430
Please rest assured, Master.

594
00:26:22,520 --> 00:26:24,190
