596
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:31,680
Since you're so talkative,

597
00:26:32,310 --> 00:26:33,590
this stew

598
00:26:33,830 --> 00:26:35,190
is the best for you.

599
00:26:43,520 --> 00:26:44,830
Have it when it's warm.

600
00:26:45,190 --> 00:26:47,640
It won't taste so good once it turns cold.

601
00:27:35,460 --> 00:27:36,760
Your sister-in-law cooks...

602
00:27:36,760 --> 00:27:37,920
So well.

603
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:42,230
The last one.

604
00:27:44,230 --> 00:27:46,640
Wen Yue, this cinnamon-vine soup is so nice.

605
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,280
Want some more?

606
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:50,590
That's enough.

607
00:27:50,590 --> 00:27:51,560
