609
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:58,640
I heard you caught the real culprit.

610
00:27:58,760 --> 00:27:59,950
It was Lady Wu.

611
00:28:00,590 --> 00:28:01,470
Does that mean

612
00:28:01,470 --> 00:28:03,110
Sun Bo has cleared his name?

613
00:28:04,110 --> 00:28:05,070
I'll go

614
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:07,000
to the Kaifeng Court and ask Inspector Gu.

615
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:09,110
Okay.

616
00:28:09,110 --> 00:28:09,920
Dig in.

617
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:11,640
I'm also stuffed.

618
00:28:13,710 --> 00:28:15,190
Enjoy the meal.

619
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:23,000
You're going to the Kaifeng Court again?

620
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,110
I'll go with you.

621
00:28:27,230 --> 00:28:28,190
I'll go

622
00:28:28,190 --> 00:28:28,950
