623
00:28:30,920 --> 00:28:31,920
What's wrong?

624
00:28:32,230 --> 00:28:33,470
Got a problem?

625
00:28:34,950 --> 00:28:36,160
I was assigned a job.

626
00:28:37,230 --> 00:28:38,710
I have to figure out

627
00:28:39,040 --> 00:28:40,350
what's going on here.

628
00:28:45,040 --> 00:28:45,830
Let's go together.

629
00:28:48,520 --> 00:28:49,520
I'll take you there.

630
00:28:55,370 --> 00:28:59,720
The weather is dry. Be careful of fire.

631
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:02,680
Are you sure this is the place?

632
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:06,560
They say all the errand boys live here.

633
00:29:06,560 --> 00:29:08,000
They must pass by from here.

634
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,710
So we can't miss him if we wait here.

635
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:17,920
It's only been one hour.

636
00:29:18,710 --> 00:29:20,280
Why are you hungry again?

637
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:27,400
You ate a lot.

638
00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:28,920
But you're hungry, too.

639
00:29:34,710 --> 00:29:35,920
Don't even think about it.

640
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,310
I bought this for Bo.

641
00:29:51,470 --> 00:29:52,640
You...

642
00:29:52,830 --> 00:29:54,190
Where did you get this?

643
00:29:54,470 --> 00:29:55,880
You never make plans

644
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:57,070
about your pocket money.

645
00:29:57,280 --> 00:29:58,830
I bought it on the way.

646
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,430
I'm going to eat it.

647
00:30:01,470 --> 00:30:03,000
Here we go.

648
00:30:14,950 --> 00:30:16,070
Take a bite.

649
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:18,830
I can't enjoy it alone

650
00:30:18,830 --> 00:30:20,280
when you're so hungry.

651
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:22,470
Thank you, Ban.

652
00:30:22,710 --> 00:30:23,800
Only one bite.

653
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:32,590
Zhao Mo, you...!

654
00:30:32,590 --> 00:30:34,280
Spit it out!

655
00:30:34,280 --> 00:30:35,160
Spit it out!

656
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:36,040
Excuse me.

657
00:30:37,190 --> 00:30:38,220
- Sorry. - Are you okay, miss?

658
00:30:38,220 --> 00:30:39,190
I'm okay.

659
00:30:39,950 --> 00:30:40,830
Are you looking for

660
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:41,760
