661
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:44,160
We're looking for Sun Bo.

662
00:30:44,230 --> 00:30:45,000
Sun Bo?

663
00:30:45,590 --> 00:30:46,350
I don't know him.

664
00:30:47,310 --> 00:30:48,950
We're looking for the errand boy.

665
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,000
Yi.

666
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:52,000
You got visitors.

667
00:30:52,950 --> 00:30:54,000
Please wait here.

668
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:55,190
Thank you.

669
00:30:55,190 --> 00:30:55,920
Thank you.

670
00:30:57,760 --> 00:30:58,760
Who is it?

671
00:31:07,520 --> 00:31:09,190
Bo and I rented this room together.

672
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:10,430
That's his bed.

673
00:31:10,560 --> 00:31:11,640
It's 300 wen per month.

674
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,520
We split the rent.

675
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,560
It's very affordable.

676
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:19,350
Why don't you sit down?

677
00:31:19,430 --> 00:31:21,280
No need.

678
00:31:21,520 --> 00:31:22,680
Where is Sun Bo?

679
00:31:22,830 --> 00:31:25,160
He must have suffered in jail these days.

680
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:26,880
He left for errands.

681
00:31:26,950 --> 00:31:28,110
You just missed him.

682
00:31:28,190 --> 00:31:30,680
He's working right after he got released?

683
00:31:30,710 --> 00:31:31,920
Is everything fine?

684
00:31:32,110 --> 00:31:32,950
Did he

685
00:31:33,070 --> 00:31:34,400
suffer in jail?

686
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:36,000
Who doesn't suffer in jail?

687
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:37,350
But people like us

688
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:38,470
can't afford to be fragile.

689
00:31:38,800 --> 00:31:40,000
How many jobs

690
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:41,310
