691
00:31:41,310 --> 00:31:42,680
He's rushing to make money.

692
00:31:43,710 --> 00:31:45,830
So where did he go?

693
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:48,950
Somewhere around Mahang Street,

694
00:31:48,950 --> 00:31:50,190
I suppose.

695
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:53,000
Then we'll take our leave.

696
00:31:53,830 --> 00:31:54,640
Take care.

697
00:31:55,590 --> 00:31:56,520
Sorry for the trouble.

698
00:31:58,160 --> 00:31:58,760
We're off.

699
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,190
I thought we were

700
00:32:05,190 --> 00:32:06,880
