702
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:13,430
that it was incomparable.

703
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:17,230
Bo's family used to be quite wealthy.

704
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:20,710
Next time you see him,

705
00:32:20,710 --> 00:32:22,830
