709
00:32:28,830 --> 00:32:30,070
Aren't you?

710
00:32:31,520 --> 00:32:32,430
So what should I do?

711
00:32:35,350 --> 00:32:37,430
Give me the rest of your money.

712
00:32:38,040 --> 00:32:40,310
I'll buy him a gift on your behalf.

713
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,800
It should be something

714
00:32:41,800 --> 00:32:42,760
he can use now.

715
00:32:53,110 --> 00:32:54,070
What else

716
00:32:54,070 --> 00:32:55,110
can I do?

717
00:32:56,590 --> 00:32:58,430
Go back and watch our father play.

718
00:32:58,560 --> 00:33:00,230
Buyou and Wen Yue went to see Inspector Gu.

719
00:33:00,430 --> 00:33:01,920
Our father is left alone.

720
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:03,350
Don't let him lose everything.

721
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:03,950
Go ahead.

722
00:33:03,950 --> 00:33:04,470
I'm off.

723
00:33:04,710 --> 00:33:05,400
Wait.

724
00:33:05,950 --> 00:33:06,680
Hold it.

725
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:10,280
Here.

726
00:33:10,800 --> 00:33:11,800
Take this with you.

727
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:15,160
Just in case you run into him.

728
00:33:19,040 --> 00:33:21,400
Do you have anything more practical here?

729
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:21,950
This one.

730
00:33:28,310 --> 00:33:28,800
Hat Demon.

731
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:29,880
The Hat Demon is back!

732
00:33:30,350 --> 00:33:31,400
Run!

733
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:37,930
Run!

734
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:39,400
The Hat Demon is here.

735
00:33:43,230 --> 00:33:44,880
The Hat Demon. Run!

736
00:33:44,950 --> 00:33:45,800
Run!

737
00:33:59,590 --> 00:34:01,680
Isn't that Commander Kang working for Zhang Qiniang?

738
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:02,880
How did he become like this?

739
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:04,110
It's him.

740
00:34:04,110 --> 00:34:05,400
It's him.

741
00:34:06,350 --> 00:34:07,640
He's dead.

742
00:34:07,710 --> 00:34:09,230
The Hat Demon killed someone again.

743
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,470
