Didn't they catch the culprit?

748
00:34:24,150 --> 00:34:25,520
I thought it was a fraud.

749
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:27,670
There's black smoke.

750
00:34:28,950 --> 00:34:31,520
It looks different from the Hat Demon last time.

751
00:34:31,950 --> 00:34:32,520
Be careful.

752
00:34:32,870 --> 00:34:34,840
It may kill someone else.

753
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:35,710
Stay away.

754
00:34:56,390 --> 00:34:58,430
I don't mind if you temper with my vegetables.

755
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:00,360
But if you touch my pine tree,

756
00:35:00,710 --> 00:35:01,800
I swear I'll kill you.

757
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:05,080
Why are you here?

758
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:07,840
Well...

759
00:35:08,080 --> 00:35:09,630
How's it going with the case

760
00:35:09,630 --> 00:35:10,520
of the Wu family?

761
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:12,710
She confessed.

762
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:13,840
She said

763
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,280
it was all her doing

764
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,670
and Wu Ao was innocent.

765
00:35:17,950 --> 00:35:18,760
What about Wu Ao?

766
00:35:19,390 --> 00:35:20,040
We let him go.

767
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:21,800
Why did you let him go?

768
00:35:21,910 --> 00:35:23,520
Lady Wu already said that...

769
00:35:24,190 --> 00:35:25,190
Wait.

770
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:28,190
My wife is here too.

771
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:30,280
She insisted on tagging along.

772
00:35:30,870 --> 00:35:31,950
Tell her as well.

773
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:32,520
Wait.

774
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:34,320
Wen Yue, come here.

775
00:35:36,150 --> 00:35:36,950
Inspector Gu

776
00:35:37,040 --> 00:35:38,360
wants to analyze the case.

777
00:35:38,520 --> 00:35:39,190
Join us there.

778
00:35:39,190 --> 00:35:40,040
I can hear you.

779
00:35:42,230 --> 00:35:42,950
Inspector Gu.

780
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:44,670
