786
00:36:01,520 --> 00:36:02,390
nor evidence.

787
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:04,670
What did she say

788
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:05,870
about the Hat Demon?

789
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:09,630
Wen Yue.

790
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:18,600
About the Hat Demon,

791
00:36:19,120 --> 00:36:20,040
Wu Qiao said

792
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:21,560
that it was all her doing.

793
00:36:22,120 --> 00:36:23,120
But

794
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,390
she couldn't clarify

795
00:36:24,390 --> 00:36:25,600
any details I asked about.

796
00:36:26,230 --> 00:36:28,080
I only know for sure

797
00:36:28,560 --> 00:36:31,040
that Lady Wu killed Wu Xiang

798
00:36:31,120 --> 00:36:32,560
on a whim.

799
00:36:32,600 --> 00:36:33,760
Meanwhile, Wu Ao

800
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:34,840
could be an accomplice.

801
00:36:34,840 --> 00:36:35,560
However,

802
00:36:36,390 --> 00:36:37,280
they have nothing

803
00:36:37,710 --> 00:36:39,040
to do with the Hat Demon.

804
00:36:40,630 --> 00:36:43,910
The Hat Demon case is a cover for their crimes.

805
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:46,800
Their whole family knows.

806
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:50,950
That's why I let go of Wu Ao.

807
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:53,080
I did it to see

808
00:36:53,430 --> 00:36:55,760
who he would meet in private.

809
00:37:00,150 --> 00:37:01,950
Brilliant move.

810
00:37:03,120 --> 00:37:04,430
You old fox.

811
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:06,040
He did well.

812
00:37:06,040 --> 00:37:07,320
It's like setting a bait.

813
00:37:08,630 --> 00:37:09,280
Wen Yue.

814
00:37:09,470 --> 00:37:10,150
Buyou.

815
00:37:12,040 --> 00:37:12,840
What's wrong, Mo?

816
00:37:13,360 --> 00:37:14,000
Easy.

817
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:14,600
That...

818
00:37:16,090 --> 00:37:16,910
- That... - Easy.

819
00:37:16,950 --> 00:37:17,910
What is it?

820
00:37:17,910 --> 00:37:18,470
The Hat Demon?

821
00:37:18,520 --> 00:37:19,910
Zhang Qiniang barged into our house

822
00:37:19,910 --> 00:37:20,870
with a group of people.

823
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:27,000
I didn't invite her.

824
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:28,280
I didn't.

825
00:37:37,760 --> 00:37:39,360
This is impressive.

826
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:40,950
So impressive.

827
00:37:41,600 --> 00:37:42,470
Look.

828
00:37:43,390 --> 00:37:44,360
The color.

829
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:45,760
Exactly.

830
00:37:46,560 --> 00:37:47,670
So luxurious.

831
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:49,950
Two horses!

832
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:54,230
Is she

833
00:37:54,230 --> 00:37:55,390
a fairy from heaven

834
00:37:55,390 --> 00:37:56,320
or

835
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,360
a lady from the palace?

836
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:59,000
So luxurious.

837
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:01,360
Laoba.

838
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:03,710
Don't you say you know many big shots?

839
00:38:04,040 --> 00:38:05,670
Do you know Zhang Qiniang?

840
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:09,840
Qiniang?

841
00:38:11,230 --> 00:38:12,320
Well...

842
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:14,840
Back when I was in the Lord's Mansion,

843
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,360
we often drank together.

844
00:38:17,430 --> 00:38:18,950
She's a lady from the palace.

845
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:21,520
The Zhao family are said to be relatives of the royal clan.

846
00:38:21,950 --> 00:38:22,950
Now I believe it.

847
00:38:22,950 --> 00:38:23,950
Me too.

848
00:38:23,950 --> 00:38:24,960
- Right? - Seriously.

849
00:38:26,560 --> 00:38:28,190
These are gold bars.

850
00:38:33,230 --> 00:38:34,120
Buyou is here.

851
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:35,800
Buyou.

852
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:37,040
Buyou, you're back.

853
00:38:37,040 --> 00:38:37,920
- Yue. - Buyou.

854
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:40,840
Buyou, what's going on?

855
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:41,600
Talk later.

856
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:42,520
Talk later.

857
00:38:43,710 --> 00:38:44,630
Move. It's my home.

858
00:38:45,430 --> 00:38:46,230
He's my brother.

859
00:38:47,430 --> 00:38:48,760
We are neighbors.

860
00:38:51,870 --> 00:38:53,230
It looks better now, right?

861
00:38:53,520 --> 00:38:54,760
So beautiful.

862
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:56,710
After your trimming,

863
00:38:56,910 --> 00:38:59,600
