865
00:39:04,230 --> 00:39:05,560
Your presence

866
00:39:05,560 --> 00:39:08,470
brings such an exuberant vibe to my humble residence.

867
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:09,120
Father.

868
00:39:10,760 --> 00:39:11,560
Shhh.

869
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:12,600
Buyou.

870
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,230
