871
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:20,230
I recall a poem by my friend.

872
00:39:20,600 --> 00:39:25,280
This mundane life is too short to spare me joyful moments.

873
00:39:25,630 --> 00:39:29,390
Who would hold on to wealth over one genuine smile?

874
00:39:29,870 --> 00:39:33,150
Holding the wine cup, I persuade the setting sun

875
00:39:33,390 --> 00:39:37,150
