876
00:39:38,360 --> 00:39:41,360
Great verses.

877
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:41,910
Father.

878
00:39:41,910 --> 00:39:42,430
I'm flattered.

879
00:39:43,230 --> 00:39:44,430
Put the verses aside

880
00:39:44,430 --> 00:39:45,520
for a second, please.

881
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:47,120
Lady Zhang.

882
00:39:47,190 --> 00:39:49,080
What are you doing at my house?

