00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:57,000
I'm going to live here.

886
00:39:58,560 --> 00:39:59,470
What's that attitude?

887
00:40:00,600 --> 00:40:01,870
We're having a guest.

888
00:40:01,870 --> 00:40:03,870
What's the fuss?

889
00:40:04,150 --> 00:40:04,760
Exactly.

890
00:40:04,760 --> 00:40:05,600
Lady Zhang.

