00:40:26,430 --> 00:40:27,190
Back to my room.

904
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,390
Wen.

905
00:40:30,630 --> 00:40:31,670
I bet you can tell.

906
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:33,230
Lady Zhang

907
00:40:33,390 --> 00:40:35,040
must be an amazing lady

