931
00:41:29,910 --> 00:41:32,870
You don't look like someone who would be afraid.

932
00:41:33,870 --> 00:41:34,470
Exactly.

933
00:41:35,520 --> 00:41:36,670
Only a fool

934
00:41:36,670 --> 00:41:38,080
is scared of nothing.

935
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:41,520
I'm in the light

936
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:43,950
while my enemy is in the dark.

937
00:41:45,600 --> 00:41:48,040
I can't be at ease.

938
00:41:50,650 --> 00:41:51,840
Now I get it.

939
00:41:52,040 --> 00:41:53,320
You wouldn't think

940
00:41:53,360 --> 00:41:55,360
