953
00:42:27,390 --> 00:42:29,360
Yue, Buyou.

954
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:31,470
One is brave and the other is wise.

955
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:33,390
When I'm with you,

956
00:42:33,470 --> 00:42:34,670
I'm sure

957
00:42:34,670 --> 00:42:37,150
that the Hat Demon won't dare to pick on me.

958
00:42:39,230 --> 00:42:40,710
Buyou, Wen Yue.

959
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:42,390
I caught the Hat Demon.

960
00:42:42,950 --> 00:42:43,670
She's my sister.

961
00:42:43,670 --> 00:42:44,760
Let me in.

962
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:48,630
What happened?

963
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:58,190
I caught the Hat Demon.

